# Parties — Gamified AI Swarm Simulations
#
# No env vars needed! Parties uses the existing sidekick infrastructure.
#
# Usage:
#   clappie parties run <game>        Start a simulation
#   clappie parties status            See active simulations
#   clappie parties roll 2d6          Roll dice
#
# Game files go in: recall/parties/games/<name>.txt
# Identity files go in: recall/parties/identities/<name>.txt
# Emerged memories auto-saved to: recall/parties/identities/emerged/<name>.txt
#
# See SKILL.md for full orchestration guide.
